extendedInfo.description: The National Society of Genetic Counselors presents the 31st Annual Education Conference (AEC). This conference is the only national event that focuses specifically on the education needs of genetic counselors and professionals interested in genetics and genomics. NSGC is expanding the spectrum of genomic health, October 24-27 in Boston, Massachusetts, with diverse education sessions and network opportunities specifically for genetic counselors and genetic professionals.This year, NSGC is delivering everything AEC directly to your finger-tips via the 2012 NSGC AEC mobile app. Gain early access to conference education, speakers and scheduling. Download the app to navigate the show floor with ease using the interactive maps, search the exhibitor directory and stay in-the-know with show alerts.
